file=AI & Agents/proto/custom/agent-prototype-kit/assets/prototype-manifest-template.md · pm—:Prototype Manifest — <name>-proto-<YYYYMMDD>=**Hypothesis (exactly one):** <what this prototype tests, falsifiably stated>\n**Proposed by:** <agent/operator> \· **Date:** <YYYY-MM-DD> \· **Expiry:** <date — default +14 days> \· **Registry entry:** <ref, state=prototype>\n · tb=\| # \| Criterion \| Measured how \| Pass bar \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| 1 \| \| \| \| · c(c:Cage (Fleet Charter Rail 4 — defaults, not editable downward)=- Sandbox: per quinn's policy, egress-allowlisted (Engineering Rail 2)\n- Tools: ONLY registered entries from relay's registry (trial grants listed): <list>\n- Data: NO production data, NO production memory layers\n- Expiry behavior: silence = archive\n · ss:Skills sketch=<what skills it would carry — drafts allowed, frontmatter required>\n · v(a:Verdict (filled at expiry by promote-or-archive-verdict)=PROMOTE (→ Rail 3 new-agent proposal) / ARCHIVE (learnings ledger ref: ) \· Date:\n